platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: It only takes about five minutes to realise just how strange Severed is. But to rescue your family, you’re going to have to dive right in, mastering the excellent swipe-based combat, travelling through a magical realm filled with danger, and—yeah—collecting some severed limbs. Like we said, it’s a little weird. But this Apple Design Award winner is also gorgeous, atmospheric and totally memorable.

2017 Apple Design Award 受賞作品。始めて5分もすれば、「Severed」がいかに奇妙な作品であるか気付くはず。それでも家族を救うため、あなたはこの世界に飛び込み、スワイプ操作による戦い方を習得しながら、危険に満ちた魔法の国を旅して行かねばなりません――切断した魔物の四肢をかき集めながら。繰り返しますが、本作は少し不気味です。しかし同時に、その美しいグラフィックと独特の雰囲気はプレイする者を魅了します。

It only takes about five minutes to realize just how strange Severed is. But to rescue your family, you’re going to have to dive right in, mastering the excellent swipe-based combat, travelling through a magical realm filled with danger, and—yeah—collecting some severed limbs. Like we said, it’s a little weird. But this Apple Design Award winner is also gorgeous, atmospheric, and totally memorable.
